16 Sanidassanattika, Upādānadukādi
Sanidassanattika, Upādānadukādi
89.
196Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ noupādānaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ nokilesaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.)
197Hetuyā tiṃsa, ārammaṇe nava…pe…  aññamaññe pañcavīsa…pe…  avigate tiṃsa.
